{"id":312881,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-张建平拆迁案上诉听证会，常州市法院内/","date":"2013-09-10T20:03:03Z","modified":"2013-09-10T20:03:03Z","title":"维权网 | 张建平拆迁案上诉听证会，常州市法院内外戒备森严（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><span></span></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>分，常州市中级人民法院对张建平诉中天钢铁集团有限公司拆迁安置协议上诉案举行听证会，张建平委托倪文华代理。旁听者众多，有南通、如皋、张家港、昆山、镇江及当地的拆迁维权人士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>多人。该院如临大敌，安检特别严格，只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>位旁听者领到旁听证，其余一概拒之门外。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div><span><span>张建平是著名维权人士，因车祸致残，坐在轮椅上帮助弱势群体维权，事迹感人至深。他还创办了《权利运动》网站，在国内外有很大的影响。听证会当天，法院从外调来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>多法警，戒备森严，营造紧张气氛。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span><span><span>听证会对中天钢铁集团有限公司是否按拆迁安置协议规定履行义务进行调查。张建平提供了证据，证明该公司未按协议规定履行安置义务。奇怪的是，该公司既不能证明自己亲自履行了协议规定的安置义务，也没有证据证明委托他人履行了安置义务。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span><span><span>各地赶来旁听的维权人士敬仰张建平的维权精神，不顾烈日暴晒，一直在法院外等候到听证会结束，已是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>点半了。大家一起与张建平一起拍照留念。</span></span></div>\n<div><span><span></span></span> </div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Qh2FMJNob2s/Ui9A73ofPSI/AAAAAAAAoEA/HvcTzJj1Y6k/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Qh2FMJNob2s/Ui9A73ofPSI/AAAAAAAAoEA/HvcTzJj1Y6k/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--J0ee9MVGt4/Ui9A8nHgGKI/AAAAAAAAoEI/GjSqE8FqfFg/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--J0ee9MVGt4/Ui9A8nHgGKI/AAAAAAAAoEI/GjSqE8FqfFg/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-B16h5UvFKrk/Ui9A-c4CvGI/AAAAAAAAoEQ/u9f51JTVwJc/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-B16h5UvFKrk/Ui9A-c4CvGI/AAAAAAAAoEQ/u9f51JTVwJc/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div> </div>\n<div><span><span></span></span> </div>\n<div><span><span></span></span> </div>\n<p><span> </span></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}